General.Name: United States Basketball League Inc
General.Description: United States Basketball League, Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, the company was engaged in developing and managing a professional basketball league, the United States Basketball League in the United States. It focuses on evaluating and assessing new business opportunities. The company was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Tampa, Florida. United States Basketball League, Inc. is a subsidiary of Meisenheimer Capital, Inc.
